results.releaseNotes:
In the standalone app:
- improved compatibility with new iPad display resolutions and aspect ratios. Now the app's interface adjusts to any screen size automatically;
- implemented portrait orientation mode support (for iPad) to comply with the new iPadOS 26 requirements. In the portrait mode, all 4 module racks are visible simultaneously on the screen together with the onscreen keyboard;
- graphics refresh rate increased to 120 FPS (where available);
- minor bug fixes.
